- iter 6: criterion #0 ŌĆö rejected at line 42 (src/auth.ts:42)


## What to do this turn
1. **Study the actual code/docs** related to this task. Do not paraphrase git log.
2. Make a concrete change OR collect verifying evidence.
3. Use these structured tags as you progress:
   - \`<evidence file="path" line="N" criterion="i" note="why this proves criterion i" />\` ŌĆö one per criterion you cover.
   - \`<evidence command="cmd" exit_code="0" criterion="i" note="..." />\` ŌĆö when verification is by shell command.
